start.label: if you can't beat them join them

examples.en: His voice was getting stronger every minute.
If you gum the tape it is stronger.
She emerged from the divorce a stronger person.
The team is stronger now they've included Roscoe.
The company needs to develop a stronger orientation towards marketing its products.
Some wool has been interwoven with the silk, to make the cloth heavier and stronger.
The uniting influence was stronger than the separative.
He'll return to work when he's feeling a little stronger.
We beat a team that was much stronger than ourselves.
The builder added supports to make the walls stronger.
Nature has seen to it that men are stronger than women.
Lash the two pieces of wood together, to make them stronger.
They are stronger than us and can afford to bide their time.
Stronger legal safeguards are needed to protect the consumer.
The firm started the new year on a stronger financial footing.
The average man is taller and stronger than the average woman.
All such sympathies were now overpowered by a stronger feeling.
If these don't work I may have to prescribe you something stronger.
Giotto was, in the make of him, a very much stronger man than Titian.
Through continued use, capabilities become stronger and more difficult for competitors to understand and imitate.
